        "data": "<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Timezones in Backups (Next Backup, Backup list, and Backup Frequency)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Deployments page shows failed deployments with In Progress status</li>\n<li>\n<span>Page does not auto-update</span> on IE11 (<span>Live details are not displayed)</span>\n</li>\n<li>Pagination is not working on Builds and Deployments pages</li>\n</ul>"
